LIST OF PLAYSTATION 2 GAMES FOR PLAYSTATION 4
This is a list of PlayStation 2 games for PlayStation 4 available from the PlayStation Store .
These are the original games , emulated at high - definition with the addition of PlayStation 4 features such as Trophies , Remote Play and Share Play .
There are currently games on this list .
